content: Me lo ense√±o un amigo. El concepto del juego es muy bueno y original, adem√°s de divertido. El modo historia entretiene, pero adem√°s con el online puedes luchar contra otros jugadores lo que lo hace m√°s diverso en cuanto a que hacer. Hay gran variedad de personajes y es de los pocos nuevos juegos actuales que realmente es bueno y no te bombardea con anuncios (Aunque evidentemente si que hay para que se pueda mantener el juego). Enhorabuena a los creadores y espero que sigan innovando con actus.
en_content: A friend taught it to me. The concept of the game is very good and original, as well as fun. The story mode is entertaining, but also with the online mode you can fight against other players which makes it more diverse in terms of what to do. There is a great variety of characters and it is one of the few current new games that is really good and doesn't bombard you with ads (although obviously there are so that the game can be maintained). Congratulations to the creators and I hope they continue to innovate with actus.
